\par
\pard\f0\fs28  ({\b a}) Subsp. {\b columnae}: Leaves subglabrous to sparsely pubescent. Bracts 5-8 mm.{\i  Throughout the range of the species}.
\par
\pard\f0\fs28  ({\b b}) Subsp. {\b gussonii}(Ten.) Rech. fil.,{\i  Bot. Arch.} ({\i Berlin}){\b  43}: 56 (1941): Leaves densely pubescent. Bracts 12-16 mm. {\i S. Italy, Sicilia.}
